  "description": {
    "zh": "下午好，雇佣兵。我们有个问题需要尽快解决。我搞到了一批M249 SAW的货，但我的小队在运输途中遭到了袭击。有些武器被抢走了。更糟的是，列出每把枪的货运清单在混乱中丢失了。我需要那份文件才能知道到底丢了什么。去海关主桥旁的虎式轻型装甲车那里，那是你最有可能找到它的地方。明白了吗？",
    "en": " Good afternoon Mercenary. We’ve got a problem that needs fixing fast. I secured a shipment of M249 SAWs but my team got hit during delivery. Some of those weapons were snatched. Worse yet the manifest listing every gun got lost in the chaos. I need that paperwork to know exactly what’s missing. Head to the Tigr LAV by the main bridge on Customs. That’s your best bet to find it. Clear? "
  },
